# RQ-53-10-01-071: Radar Antenna Mounting

## Requirement Statement
The nose cone shall provide mounting interface for weather radar antenna with precise alignment.

## Acceptance Criteria
- Mounting bracket bolted to forward bulkhead
- Alignment tolerance Â±0.5 degrees
- Vibration isolation to protect radar
- Load capacity 20 kg (radar antenna weight)

## Compliance Status
ICD with radar supplier released
